  "description": "Are you bored from hearing the minecraft sounds ? Then it is for you It Adds haul effect to every sound and makes sounds better.",
  "body": "<p><strong>\"Aesthetic Sounds\" is a Minecraft PE resource pack that introduces a hall effect to every sound, creating a rich acoustic experience. It also features unique sounds for block breaking and sword hits, enhancing the game's audio landscape and immersing players in a vibrant, dynamic environment as they explore and battle.</strong></p>\n<h2>Showcase Video--</h2>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/X0H8ooIORJo?si=SQUacZ0jxRxU7fy4\" width=\"560\" height=\"314\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe><br>&nbsp;<strong>Features -</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Hall Effect on All Sounds &ndash; Adds spacious, echoing acoustics to every in-game sound for a richer atmosphere.</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Custom Block Breaking Sounds &ndash; Unique audio feedback for breaking different blocks, adding realism and variety.</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Distinct Sword Hit Sounds &ndash; Enhanced combat audio with sharper, more impactful sword strike sounds.</li>\n<li>Immersive Audio Overhaul &ndash; Transforms the game&rsquo;s soundscape into a more dynamic and engaging experience.</li>\n<li>No more scary sounds</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Socials:</span></strong></h1>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Join our discord&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://discord.gg/mYfhfWtH8v\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><u><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1238974/description_ab71df94-6fc9-41c3-ae8b-b021beb72514.png\" alt=\"Discord\"></u></a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@NetherSparkStudios\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">✅ Allowed with My Projects</a></strong></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li><strong>You can showcase my work in videos/streams if you give proper credit (e.g., link to the official download).</strong></li>\n<li><strong>You can edit file for personal use only</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>❌ Not Allowed with My Projects</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You cannot distribute through monetized links (AdFly, Linkvertise, etc.).</strong></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You cannot edit and re-share my projects .</strong></li>\n</ul>",
